Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着…  或者说这样反而有戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戏有戏
