Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戏的对吧
